Package: figures2
Type: Package
Title: A package to support a variety of figure production tasks
Version: 1.00
Date: 2015-01-26
Author: Greg Cicconetti, David Wade
URL: https://github.com/gcicc/figures2
Maintainer: Greg Cicconetti <greg.2.cicconetti@gsk.com>
Description: This package takes the view that a figure is a collection of
    graphs/tables assembled on a page and optionally annotated with metadata
    (titles, headers and footers).  Functions and supporting documentation are
    offered to streamline a variety of figure production task.
License: GPL-2
LazyLoad: yes
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2), survival, ggplot2(>= 1.0.0), scales
Imports: plyr (>= 1.7.1), digest, grid (>= 3.0.0), gridExtra, gtable (>= 0.1.1), reshape2, stringr (>= 0.6.2), gtable (>= 0.1.2),  RColorBrewer 
ByteCompile: TRUE
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown